{"type": "article", "id": 16559, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-26T06:48:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17737, "name": "tripleliving studio"}, {"id": 15825, "name": "United Nude"}, {"id": 17738, "name": "iumbrella"}, {"id": 17739, "name": "First String"}, {"id": 17740, "name": "Aaron Saxton"}, {"id": 17741, "name": "Rem D Koolhaas"}, {"id": 17742, "name": "Iyad Naja"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000345JqwB2A75ktEPi1xF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t山石软泥灯 by tripleliving studio\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t越来越的设计团队喜欢开发混凝土的设计美感，台湾的 tripleliving 团队曾经创造了一种软水泥材质，让水泥温和柔软。而这盏山石软泥灯则是在其基础上的再创新，他们保留了硅胶材质和水泥纹路，用手工灌制的方式调配透光比例，让光芒能够透出来，改变了原本印象中的机械冰冷的水泥。而圆锥体的外形像一座小山，使这盏灯有了沉静内敛的气质，让人静下心来观察纹路。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/tripleliving-ms\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003455Wvo6nTlPs0OhiKFB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003456mtAzC2KBq4wNf7UZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003456a6KZcNxrnCt83Eog.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003456yPIOHh23LiaY9JNS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060034579CNIOqTt21o3Xjvm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t工具尺 by Aaron Saxton\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是把自带切割功能的尺子，它在常规的尺子下面加了一个底座，中间用弹簧转轴相连。而纸张就放在尺子和底座中间，再用弹簧调整纸它们的距离，就可以切割纸张了。这把尺子可以容纳6毫米的宽度，它实际代替了切割垫，不会伤到桌面，使用灵活，且非常节约空间。目前还没有售卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003457AOS4c1JsHdhTgX3y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003458YotS1VRLMcNw6EIb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060034587RSWsNBjZXFbgHw2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003459DBY5fCGUJqQkxZtH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003459J8ZtGoSIgQAdUv53.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t“stealth”保护壳 by United Nude\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰建筑师 Rem D Koolhaas 创立的英国品牌 United Nude，近期推出了新品“stealth”保护壳，专门放置 12 寸的电子产品。在黑色皮革的外壳上覆盖了一层亚光橡胶涂料，有柔和的光泽和质感。四个边角有立体的处理，显得简洁大方。重要的是它兼有防水防震的功能。售价 149 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.unitednude.com/stealth-sleeve-black-80-pu-20-cow-leather-2825\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003500boyrALhItglNfs9u.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003500aCtU5dQJ4x78skYy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80440098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600350060EhwB1LKQYS8Wzn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003501X3LDsx0FjT2CG8Np.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003501rGvNdBQ5hpaPHJq8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.23838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t翻转雨伞 by iumbrella\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一把翻转伞，它的伞面是反向的，如果只是稍微淋过雨的雨伞，雨水就完全收在伞里而不会滴出来。它更特别之处在于弯曲的手把可以拆解下来双向安装，因而当雨伞淋过大雨或需要滴水的时候，就可以拆下来装在另一头让它自然滴落。设计者是为了解决雨伞到处滴水，导致地面过去潮湿的问题，这把翻转伞让滴水变得可控。产品目前在众筹，有蓝色和紫色两款，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/iumbrella\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003502ctB3LaEuAj8Xis6l.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5037594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003502cntjXu1C68mT3i9v.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79491525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003503wcDA69H0d7YE5rZs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9025\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003503LkQwY0WHrCxspaVX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9025\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003503Kk85W6SRYZtJnwl1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t坐凳 by Iyad Naja\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是黎巴嫩设计师 Iyad Naja 带来的坐凳系列，正在迪拜设计周上展出。他用金属材质将阿拉伯字体做成镂空的图案，嵌在混凝土的坐凳中，有一种丰富的层次感，也是传统与现代的结合。阿拉伯文字的图案组成富有中东气息的装饰，华丽而有艺术感，并凸显出了材质的特征。这组凳子有金色、黑色和玫瑰色三种颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035047ArmlwZaFEL0yDxf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003504sv8w6WzpRVPZ9d3y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035055McGiajpzUfv4Cnd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003505tPlKQAcjZqpW9HFk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003506U5OEDnNpw2im8gYz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003506a4fredkLtX3zUHWY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32518337\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSpace系列 by  First String \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是 First String 推出的 Chuck Taylor All Star ‘70 太空系列，以 1970 年代经典的  Converse 鞋为蓝本，加入那个年代狂热的太空漫游的主题。黑白款直接从宇航员的衣服样式提取灵感，而米色圆圈款型源于打开的降落伞，在流行样式中显得与众不同。近期会在门店销售，定价 120 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003507hro3sHcWXLFumtyn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035074JjqGobtaXemdkv9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003508qIkLe9mAn3VNXRJQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035085dVNCZvq2Azsh9X4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035096UOAY04wX7W1eLQr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003509aFABJreQ3Gd78mz0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}